Package fi.tuni.mentalsurvival

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EndScreen
    This class contains game end screen, which is shown when the player has finished the game.
    GameClass
    This class contains rendering of the game, HUD, sounds, etc.
    GameObject
    This class is used to create game objects such as shelter.
    GameObjectInfo
    This class contains info about the bodies created in our tiled map.
    GameUtil
    Game utility class that contains methods for different actions in game (creating the world.
    Hud
    This class contains the on-screen HUD including e.g sanity bar, joystick, story dialogs.
    JoystickControl
    The game's on screen joystick controller made with scene2d's Touchpad.
    MentalSurvival
    The actual game class that is used to create a game object.
    MenuScreen
    This class contains the main menu screen of the game.
    Player
    Player class contains all the methods and information about the player in the game.
    SplashScreen
    This class contains the splash screen which is shown to the user first when the game is opened.
    Util
    This class contains some utility methods that are not directly related to the gameplay itself.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GameObjectType
    Enum type that assigns the type to each game object's body.
